videos.description: Maryland lines up on offense and leaves an offensive guard spot empty in honor of deceased teammate Jordan McNair.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Maryland leaves O-Line spot empty in honor of McNair) 2018/9/1

videos.headline: Maryland leaves O-Line spot empty in honor of McNair

videos.description: Texas quarterback Sam Ehlinger drops a dime to wide receiver Devin Duvernay for a 39-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas WR makes beautiful diving catch for 39-yard TD

videos.description: Texas defensive back Gary Johnson is ejected for targeting with an illegal hit to the head of Maryland quarterback Kasim Hill.
videos.headline: Longhorn DB ejected for targeting

videos.description: Terps wide receiver Jeshaun Jones completes a 20-yard touchdown to Taivon Jones, giving Jeshaun a rushing, receiving, and passing touchdown in the first half.
videos.headline: Maryland WR completes TD trifecta

videos.description: The Terps fail on a  jet sweep and Texas recovers the ball in the end zone for a safety.
videos.headline: Maryland mishap results in Texas safety

videos.description: Maryland true freshman Jeshaun Jones contributes to touchdowns three different ways in the first half of his first college game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Jones runs, catches and throws for TDs) 2018/9/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones runs, catches and throws for TDs

videos.description: Texas stuffs Maryland's quarterback sneak attempt on fourth down from its own 37-yard line.
videos.headline: Longhorns stuff the Terps on 4th down

videos.description: Longhorn quarterback Sam Ehlinger hits wide receiver Collin Johnson for a 33-yard pass, setting up a 2-yard rushing touchdown for running back Kyle Porter.
videos.headline: Perfect sideline pass sets up 2-yard TD for Texas

videos.description: Maryland executes a jet sweep to perfection as running back Tayon Fleet-Davis speeds in for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Terps strike back to open 4th quarter

videos.description: Texas vs. Maryland has been delayed because of severe thunderstorms in the area with 14:25 remaining in the game.
videos.headline: Texas-Maryland game delayed because of weather

videos.description: Antoine Brooks intercepts Sam Ehlinger late in the fourth quarter to clinch Maryland's upset of Texas in an emotional season opener.
